        <h1>Pi Cortex Zero Data Retention Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Last Updated: April 25, 2026</strong></p>
        
        <h2>1. Data We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect only @pi username and wallet address via Pi SDK for authentication and payments.</p>
        
        <h2>2. Data We Don't Collect</h2>
        <p>We don't store goal content. All goals are encrypted locally on your device and deleted after 24h.</p>
        
        <h2>3. No Third-Party Analytics</h2>
        <p>We do not use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, or any third-party tracking.</p>
        
        <h2>4. User Data Deletion</h2>
        <p>User can delete all data instantly from within the app. No data is retained on our servers.</p>
        
        <h2>5. Smart Contract</h2>
